e way. <\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/20269&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121349\/tips-sustainable-travel.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121349\/tips-sustainable-travel-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121349\/tips-sustainable-travel-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Sustainable Travel Tips &#x2013; 10 Easy Tips for You to Use Now!\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Many tour companies are focusing on the future of sustainable travel:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Intrepid Travel &#x2013; has been carbon neutral since 2010.<\/li><li>Fairbnb &#x2013; Donates 50% of the profits into community projects. <\/li><li>B&#x2019;n&#x2019;Tree &#x2013; Plant a tree for every booking you make (and are partnered up with <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Booking.com (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/booking\/\" target=\"_blank\">Booking.com<\/a> and <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Skyscanner (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/skyscanner\/\" target=\"_blank\">Skyscanner<\/a>).<\/li><\/ul>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-3-pack-light-easy-sustainable-travel-tip\">3. Pack light &#x2013; Easy Sustainable Travel Tip<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Packing lightly and thoughtfully is a small, yet effective way, of helping with sustainable travel. The more we pack, the more fuel planes, trains, and automobiles will need. It&#x2019;s also easier to carry lighter luggage. Try to halve what&#x2019;s in your bag by carefully thinking about what you&#x2019;re packing. For example:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Pack a refillable water bottle, or a water purifier, to save you from buying single-use plastic.<\/li><li>Try to pack eco-friendly products, or go completely plastic-free, by using shampoo bars, tooth tabs, deodorant bars, etc. They use up less space, are much better for the environment and are allowed in your hand luggage.<\/li><li>Bring your own food on the flight. Airplane meals are generally served with a lot of single-use plastic.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121353\/sustainable-travel-shampoo-bar.jpg\" alt=\"sustainable travel shampoo bar\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"330\" alt=\"sustainable travel shampoo bar\" class=\"wp-image-21514 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121353\/sustainable-travel-shampoo-bar.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/