\n\n<ul><li>Bring your own cutlery and straw. This saves on single-use plastic given at cafes and markets.<\/li><li>Consider bringing a kindle or an iPad to read books on. Books will make your luggage much heavier.<\/li><li>Think about your clothing. Pack thin materials, that can be rolled up very small to utilize space.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121452\/reusable-straws-575x810.jpg\" alt=\"reusable straws\"><\/noscript><img width=\"240\" height=\"338\" alt=\"reusable straws\" class=\"wp-image-21449 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121452\/reusable-straws-575x810.jpg 575w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121452\/reusable-straws-300x423.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121452\/reusable-straws-600x846.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121452\/reusable-straws-426x600.jpg 426w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121452\/reusable-straws-240x338.jpg 240w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121452\/reusable-straws-1090x1536.jpg 1090w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121452\/reusable-straws-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121452\/reusable-straws-116x163.jpg 116w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121452\/reusable-straws-128x180.jpg 128w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121452\/reusable-straws-545x768.jpg 545w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-c