36.jpg 1090w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121459\/bamboo-cutlery-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121459\/bamboo-cutlery-116x163.jpg 116w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121459\/bamboo-cutlery-128x180.jpg 128w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121459\/bamboo-cutlery-545x768.jpg 545w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121459\/bamboo-cutlery-726x1024.jpg 726w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121459\/bamboo-cutlery-766x1080.jpg 766w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121459\/bamboo-cutlery-1022x1440.jpg 1022w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121459\/bamboo-cutlery.jpg 1362w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121459\/bamboo-cutlery-21x30.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121459\/bamboo-cutlery-575x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-4-avoid-animal-entertainment\">4. <strong>Avoid animal entertainment<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Wildlife is one of the best parts of traveling. Sadly, 75% of all <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/wildlife-tourism\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">wildlife tourism<\/a> has a negative effect on animals. Taking part in animal entertainment can mean anything as obvious as watching dolphins performing tricks, to riding an elephant. It also applies to entertainment that seems innocent, like feeding an eagle, holding a snake, or trying Luwak coffee.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Here are the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/wildlife-tourism\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">things to know about wildlife tourism and the better alternatives<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121422\/travel-animal-cruelty-531x810.jpg\" alt=\"travel animal cruelty\"><\/noscript><img width=\"221\" height=\"338\" alt=\"travel animal cruelty\" class=\"wp-image-21489 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 531px) 100vw, 531px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121422\/travel-animal-cruelty-531x810.jpg 531w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121422\/travel-animal-cruelty-300x458.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121422\/travel-animal-cruelty-600x916.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121422\/travel-animal-cruelty-393x600.jpg 393w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121422\/travel-animal-cruelty-221x338.jpg 221w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121422\/travel-animal-cruelty-1006x1536.jpg 10