440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123922\/elephants-yala-national-park-sri-lanka-30x20.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123922\/elephants-yala-national-park-sri-lanka.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Animal feeding<\/strong><br>Feeding wild animals is not a good idea, because they may become dependent on food supplies if they are fed by tourists.&#xA0;Looking after wildlife in these ways helps sustain travel for the future.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip<\/strong>: A positive way to care for animals is by volunteering at a certified animal rescue center. (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.sanctuaryfederation.org\/find-a-sanctuary\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"See all locations (opens in a new tab)\">See all locations<\/a>)<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121426\/snake-cruelty.jpg\" alt=\"snake cruelty\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"338\" alt=\"snake cruelty\" class=\"wp-image-21488 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121426\/snake-cruelty.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121426\/snake-cruelty-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121426\/snake-cruelty-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121426\/snake-cruelty-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121426\/snake-cruelty-1080x810.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121426\/snake-cruelty-450x338.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121426\/snake-cruelty-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121426\/snake-cruelty-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121426\/snake-cruelty-163x122.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121426\/snake-cruelty-240x180.jpg 240w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121426\/snake-cruelty-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121426\/snake-cruelty-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121426\/snake-cruelty-1440x1080.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121426\/snake-cruelty-30x23.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121426\/snake-cruelty.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-5-be-respectful-of-the-environment\">5. Be<strong> respectful of the environment<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Respecting the environment ensures the future of sustainable travel. Over time, beautiful natural areas are seeing the effects of mass tourism. <br><br>For instance, avoid touching ancient temples and recognize that trails and fences are there for a reason. In short: read the signs.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Coral bleaching is another worldwide problem. Due to this, only look at the corals from a distance and never touch them. By doing this, coral growth is hoped to increase. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Another important and easy change is making sure to wear <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/reef-safe-sunscreen\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">reef-safe sunscreen<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121448\/sustainable-travel-coral-reef.jpg\" alt=\"sustainable travel coral reef\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"316\" alt=\"sustainable travel coral reef\" class=\"wp-image-21451 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121448\/sustainable-travel-coral-reef.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121448\/sustainable-travel-coral-reef-300x211.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121448\/sustainable-travel-coral-reef-600x421.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121448\/sustainable-travel-coral-reef-800x562.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121448\/sustainable-travel-coral-reef-1080x758.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121448\/sustainable-travel-coral-reef-450x316.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121448\/sustainable-travel-coral-reef-1536x1078.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121448\/sustainable-travel-coral-reef-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121448\/sustainable-travel-coral-reef-163x114.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121448\/sustainable-travel-coral-reef-256x180.jpg 256w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121448\/sustainable-travel-coral-reef-768x539.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121448\/sustainable-travel-coral-reef-1024x719.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121448\/sustainable-travel-coral-reef-1440x1011.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121448\/sustainable-travel-coral-reef-30x21.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121448\/sustainable-travel-coral-reef.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-6-leave-tracks-not-trash-make-travel-sustainable\">6. <strong>Leave tracks not trash<\/strong> &amp; make travel sustainable<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Protect animals and sea life from getting entangled and ingesting plastic toxins, or even prevent <a aria-label=\"microplastics to end up in our food chain (opens in a new tab)\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.chemistryworld.com\/news\/humans-consuming-thousands-of-microplastic-particles-in-their-food-every-year\/3010600.article\" target=\"_blank\">microplastics from ending up in our food<\/a>. It is a relatively simple task to throw your garbage in designated bins. Remember that plastic can take up to 1000 years to decompose! As a result, it&#x2019;s best to use compostable alternatives, avoid buying plastic, or <a aria-label=\"travel plastic-free (opens in a new tab)\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/reduce-plastic-travel\/\" target=\"_blank\">travel plastic-free<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121455\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle-2.jpg\" alt=\"reusable water bottle\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"reusable water bottle\" class=\"wp-image-21448 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121455\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle-2.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121455\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121455\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle-2-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121455\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle-2-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121455\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle-2-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121455\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle-2-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121455\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle-2-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121455\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle-2-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121455\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle-2-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121455\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle-2-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121455\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121455\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121455\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle-2-1440x961.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121455\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle-2-30x20.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121455\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle-2.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Positive action, such as picking up litter is a fantastic way to help. Beach clean-ups are happening all over the world, so have a look online to see where your nearest one is. This is a great way to be a part of positive change, help the community and meet new people who are interested in sustainable travel!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Here&#x2019;s <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/reduce-plastic-travel\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"how to use less plastic while traveling (opens in a new tab)\">how to use less plastic while traveling<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121438\/plastic-free-travel-535x810.jpg\" alt=\"plastic free travel\"><\/noscript><img width=\"223\" height=\"338\" alt=\"plastic free travel\" class=\"wp-image-21455 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 535px) 100vw, 535px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121438\/plastic-free-travel-535x810.jpg 535w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121438\/plastic-free-travel-300x454.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121438\/plastic-free-travel-600x908.jpg 600w, 