\/03\/23121435\/sustainable-travel-beach-cleanup.jpg 1269w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121435\/sustainable-travel-beach-cleanup-20x30.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121435\/sustainable-travel-beach-cleanup-535x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-7-shop-locally\">7. <strong>Shop local<\/strong>ly<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sustainable travel is about having a positive effect on your destination, its culture, and the community. One way to do this is by shopping at businesses that are locally owned.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Food<\/strong><br>Find local markets for food that is locally sourced. This is different from the big supermarkets that import food via planes, contributing greatly to carbon emissions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121432\/sustainable-travel-shop-local.jpg\" alt=\"sustainable travel shop local\"><\/noscript><img width=\"418\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sustainable travel shop local\" class=\"wp-image-21458 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121432\/sustainable-travel-shop-local.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121432\/sustainable-travel-shop-local-300x243.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121432\/sustainable-travel-shop-local-600x486.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121432\/sustainable-travel-shop-local-741x600.jpg 741w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121432\/sustainable-travel-shop-local-1001x810.jpg 1001w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121432\/sustainable-travel-shop-local-418x338.jpg 418w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121432\/sustainable-travel-shop-local-1536x1243.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121432\/sustainable-travel-shop-local-30x24.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121432\/sustainable-travel-shop-local-163x132.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121432\/sustainable-travel-shop-local-222x180.jpg 222w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121432\/sustainable-travel-shop-local-768x622.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121432\/sustainable-travel-shop-local-1024x829.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121432\/sustainable-travel-shop-local-1334x1080.jpg 1334w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121432\/sustainable-travel-shop-local-1779x1440.jpg 1779w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121432\/sustainable-travel-shop-local-30x24.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121432\/sustainable-travel-shop-local.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Clothing<\/strong><br>Likewise, fast fashion is badly affecting the planet. Try to adopt a minimalist approach and ask yourself <em>&#x2018;do I really need this?&#x2019;<\/em>. If you feel like you absolutely must buy those shoes, make sure to shop second hand.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Must-read: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/netherlands\/vintage-stores-amsterdam\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Amsterdam Vintage Shopping Guide<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23122444\/citytrip-things-to-do-rotterdam-vintage-shopping-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"citytrip things to do rotterdam vintage shopping\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"citytrip things to do rotterdam vintage shopping\" class=\"wp-image-20060 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23122444\/citytrip-things-to-do-rotterdam-vintage-shopping-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/23122444\/citytrip-things-to-do-rotterdam-vintage-shopping-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltino