"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip: <\/strong>When visiting your local street market, it&#x2019;s a good idea to bring your own reusable bags\/containers with you so you don&#x2019;t need to use plastic bags.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-8-save-energy-water\">8. <strong>Save Energy &amp; Water<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A lot of effort is made to save energy and water at home and these efforts can continue throughout our travels. Here&#x2019;s how:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Energy<\/strong><br>Protecting our resources is a huge part of sustainable travel. Save energy whilst traveling by:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><em>Unplugging<\/em> &#x2013; don&#x2019;t leave items on standby and turn the lights off. <\/li><li><em>Temperature control &#x2013;<\/em> Turn the heating down when leaving, turn off your air conditioning and adjust your refrigerator&#x2019;s temperature.  These use a huge amount of energy!<\/li><li><em>Close the curtains<\/em> &#x2013; This keeps the heat out so you don&#x2019;t need as much power from your air conditioning.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel.jpg\" alt=\"sustainable travel\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"sustainable travel\" class=\"wp-image-21453 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-1080x719.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-1536x1023.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-1440x959.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel-30x20.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121442\/sustainable-travel.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Water<\/strong><br>Saving water has never been more important. Water resources are low, and less than 1% of water worldwide is currently usable. Conserve water by:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<ul><li><em>Leaving the &#x2018;do not disturb&#x2019; sign on the door<\/em> &#x2013; meaning that housekeeping in your hotel won&#x2019;t wash your towels and sheets. <\/li><li><em>Rewear your clothing more than once<\/em> &#x2013; or handwash.  <\/li><li><em>Have a shower once a day for less than 2 minutes<\/em> &#x2013; traveling somewhere warm? Have cold showers instead!<\/li><li><em>Choose food that doesn&#x2019;t require much water to be cooked<\/em> &#x2013; so avoid rice and pasta.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Fact:<\/strong> Laundry is 16% of a hotel&#x2019;s water bill!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-9-eat-a-little-less-meat\">9. <strong>Eat a little less meat<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Meat has proven to be one of the biggest causes of climate change, therefore, decreasing meat intake has a huge positive change. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121359\/vegetarian-diet-environment-friendly.jpg\" alt