nk.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121419\/best-restaurants-canggu-i-am-breakfast-1080x746.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-10-change-the-way-you-travel\">10. <strong>Change the way you travel<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The airplane has opened up the world, by making it easier for us to get from A to B and to travel to places we otherwise wouldn&#x2019;t be able to. However, they use a lot of fuel, so they have extremely high carbon emissions.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Short flights can be short rides too!<\/strong><br>If you can, avoid flying, by taking buses and trains. Countries are renewing their rail systems, so now more overnight routes are available between countries. For this reason, research if a bus or train ride is available as well.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel.jpg\" alt=\"sustainable train travel\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"301\" alt=\"sustainable train travel\" class=\"wp-image-21511 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel-300x201.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel-600x402.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel-800x535.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel-1080x723.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel-450x301.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel-1536x1028.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel-269x180.jpg 269w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel-768x514.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel-1024x685.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel-1440x964.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel-30x20.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121356\/sustainable-train-travel.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-will-flying-ever-be-seen-as-a-form-of-sustainable-travel\"><strong>Will flying ever be seen as a form of &#x2018;sustainable travel&#x2019;?<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Unfortunately, flying will not be sustainable anytime soon. But the good news is certain airlines now give you the option to carbon offset your flight. This involves the airline investing money in other environmental projects, to balance out their flight emissions. Carbon offsetting has its critics (people aren&#x2019;t always sure where the money goes) and it definitely doesn&#x2019;t solve carbon emissions. However, right now it is the best option to help if choosing to fly. <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Skyscanner (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/skyscanner\/\" target=\"_blank\">Skyscanner<\/a> also now shows which flights are the green travel choice, based on CO2 emissions.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>The slow travel method<\/strong><br>Once at your destination try the<em> slow travel method<\/em>, by taking things easy and walking or cycling. Spend more time at one destination, rather than rushing through the country. This method is a great way to really understand local life and customs! Take public buses or car share between destinations if you are traveling around a country. A great option is Bla Bla Car and Flixbus. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip: <\/strong>For tips and tricks on how to improve, think about using a carbon footprint calculator like this one. <a href=\"https:\/\/footprint.wwf.org.uk\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https:\/\/footprint.wwf.org.uk\/<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121130\/travel-carbon-footprint-calculator-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"travel carbon footprint calculator\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"232\" alt=\"travel carbon footprint calculator\" class=\"wp-image-22187 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121130\/travel-carbon-footprint-calculator-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121130\/travel-carbon-footprint-calculator-scaled-300x154.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121130\/travel-carbon-footprint-calculator-scaled-600x309.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121130\/travel-carbon-footprint-calculator-800x412.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121130\/travel-carbon-footprint-calculator-1080x556.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121130\/travel-carbon-footprint-calculator-450x232.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121130\/travel-carbon-footprint-calculator-1536x791.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121130\/travel-carbon-footprint-calculator-2048x1055.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121130\/travel-carbon-footprint-calculator-30x15.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121130\/travel-carbon-footprint-calculator-163x84.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121130\/travel-carbon-footprint-calculator-320x165.jpg 320w, https:\/\/st